Achievements.Name: Wiper
Achievements.Description: Succesfully cheat once.

Achievements.Name: Unbreakable
Achievements.Description: Win a round without losing a teammate in a 5-on-5 or bigger match-up.

Achievements.Name: Bromance
Achievements.Description: Win a split-screen round where neither you nor your buddy are eliminated.

Achievements.Name: Lonewolf
Achievements.Description: Win a 7-on-7 or higher non-reinsertion game where you eliminate all opponents.

Achievements.Name: Sharpshooter
Achievements.Description: Get three or more eliminations in a round with over 25% accuracy.

Achievements.Name: Paint Monger
Achievements.Description: Shoot 10,000 paintballs.

Achievements.Name: Demolitionist
Achievements.Description: Eliminate three or more opponents with a single grenade.

Achievements.Name: Olympian
Achievements.Description: Dive or slide 100 times.

Achievements.Name: One Hit Wonder
Achievements.Description: Win a round with 3+ eliminations using a marker without having to reload in a 5v5 or larger match.

Achievements.Name: Bottom Feeder
Achievements.Description: Win a round entirely from the prone position.

Achievements.Name: Go Ballistic
Achievements.Description: Eliminate an opponent that you can't see using the paintballs' trajectory.

Achievements.Name: Spy
Achievements.Description: Shoot an opponent in the back from their own side of the field.

Achievements.Name: Pump Assassin
Achievements.Description: Using a pump-gun, eliminate 3 or more opponents in a round without missing.

Achievements.Name: Cross Training
Achievements.Description: Win a woodsball and a speedball tournament.

Achievements.Name: Goggler
Achievements.Description: Eliminate three opponents by shooting them in the goggles in a single round.

Achievements.Name: Lucky Clip
Achievements.Description: Eliminate an entire enemy team using a single pistol clip in a non-reinsertion game.

Achievements.Name: Team Captain
Achievements.Description: Win a round where you issue field commands to at least 3 teammates.

Achievements.Name: Connoisseur
Achievements.Description: Purchase all gear.

Achievements.Name: Mr. Popular
Achievements.Description: Play games with teammates from 50 real teams.

Achievements.Name: Billboard
Achievements.Description: Win an event while using the jersey, pants and marker from the same manufacturer.

Achievements.Name: Speedball Champion
Achievements.Description: Complete all Speedball events.

Achievements.Name: Master Woodsman
Achievements.Description: Complete all Woodsball Events.

Achievements.Name: Jack of All Trades
Achievements.Description: Complete all Recball Events.

Achievements.Name: Paintball Legend
Achievements.Description: Complete all 3 event tracks

Achievements.Name: E'Ventual Evaporation
Achievements.Description: Eliminate three opponents in a single round with a completely fogged mask.

Achievements.Name: World's Greatest Paintballer
Achievements.Description: Complete all events on Hard.

Achievements.Name: Tactical Overkill
Achievements.Description: Eliminate an opposing flag carrier with a rocket.

Achievements.Name: Lawlessness
Achievements.Description: Successfully cheat five times in a row without failing.

Achievements.Name: Foam Cowboy
Achievements.Description: Win a round while wearing the Rodeo King mask.
